; The inferred (elided) counter-leg should adopt the commodity's canonical
; style. For a right-side, digit-grouped commodity like EUR, hledger infers
; `-1,000.00 EUR` (side R, comma groups); our engine falls back to a bare
; left-side style. Distilled from numbers.test / directive-decimal-mark.test.
2017-01-01
    a   1,000.00 EUR
    b
